title: Alive and Kicking AKA Alive 'N Kickin' (320)
description:
Alive 'N Kickin' (MP3 @ 320)

Alive and Kicking, later renamed to Alive 'N Kickin', was a relatively unknown septet from New York.  Their sole claim to fame was the hit "Tighter, Tighter", which went to number 7 in 1970.
